# Environment Variables

## Database
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/coachconnect"

## Firebase Configuration (Choose ONE method)

### Method 1: Service Account File Path (Recommended for Development)
# Path relative to project root
FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PATH="./config/firebase-service-account.json"

### Method 2: Service Account JSON String (Recommended for Production/Docker)
# Paste the entire JSON content as a single-line string
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON='{"type":"service_account","project_id":"your-project","private_key_id":"...","private_key":"...","client_email":"...","client_id":"...","auth_uri":"...","token_uri":"...","auth_provider_x509_cert_url":"...","client_x509_cert_url":"..."}'

### Method 3: Application Default Credentials (For Google Cloud)
# Leave both above empty to use application default credentials

### Optional: Project ID for validation
# FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID="your-firebase-project-id"

### Legacy (Deprecated)
# FIREBASE_SECRETS="true"

